c("In a sauce, reduce demi-glace (or broth) by half.", "In a separate pan,", "saute  peppers and ginger with the brown sugar.", "Unglaze with the marsala wine and  reduce until almost all liquid is gone. Add the broth.", "Reduce by half.", "Add  soy sauce and lemon juice. KIWI PUREE-Peel and chop kiwi.", "Cook kiwi and  sugar over a low flame until the sugar starts to break down.", "Deglaze with  white wine. Reduce and add water.", "Reduce again by half.", "Puree and strain.", "PASTA PANCAKES-Cook cappellini until just a little past done. Drain pasta.", 
